data.description: NEW ROOF 2023, HVAC 2022, DECK 2023, NEW APPLIANCES. Charming full-brick 4-bedroom home in a highly sought-after location near Liberty Middle School and James Clemens High School. The open floor plan creates an inviting and spacious atmosphere, perfect for family gatherings. The large eat-in kitchen has granite countertops and plenty of storage, making it a chef's delight. Gas fireplace in the family room and beautiful LVP flooring throughout. Isolated master with a large en suite bathroom. Outside, the generous lot has a privacy fence and deck ideal for outdoor entertaining. 10x20 shed remains. This home is a true gem, combining comfort convenience in an unbeatable location.
